vote.title: Authorize a Public Highway At-grade Crossing Improvement Agreement with the Union Pacific Railroad Company for the widening, improvement and maintenance of the Chalk Hill Road at-grade public road crossing between Interstate Highway-30 Frontage Road and Singleton Boulevard - Not to exceed $1,308,399.00 - Financing: Street and Transportation Improvement Funds (2012 General Obligation Bond Fund)
